org.apache.struts2.portlet.servlet

Class PortletHttpSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.struts2.portlet.servlet.PortletHttpSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.http.HttpSession

    public class PortletHttpSession
extends Object
implements javax.servlet.http.HttpSession
    Wrapper object exposing a PortletSession as a HttpSession instance. Clients accessing this session object will in fact operate on the PortletSession object wrapped by this session object.
